Package: spatula
Title: Utilities for Working with Spatial Data
Version: 0.98.0
Date: 2020-04-27
Description:
    Provides Bioconductor-friendly bindings for classes from the sp package,
    allowing them to be stored as metadata fields on standard Bioconductor objects 
    like the SummarizedExperiment container.
Depends: 
    sp,
    S4Vectors,
    IRanges
Imports:
    BiocGenerics
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    BiocStyle,
    testthat
